    "During this stage, we excluded irrelevant sections such as tables of contents, prefaces, acknowledgements, pictures, references, and appendices.",
    "➁ Question GenerationThe chunks were fed to GPT-3.5-turbo to generate ten questions and corresponding multiple-choice answers for every 8,000 tokens.",
